Eligibility for Prize

The winning submissions/solutions will only be eligible for the awards if

  • all source code and additional data sets used will be made openly available to be published under the GNU GPLv3 license on the Challenge github account.
  • use of external dataset is permitted if open data and documented.

  • the solution is original: teams must use their own original solutions.
